    <title>Char Burn Char</title>
  </head>
  <body>


    <div id="instruct">
    <p>HOW TO PLAY</p>
    </div>

    <div id="play">
    <p>Press <span class="red">'S'</span> to start and <span class="red">'P'</span> to pause</p>
    <p>Kill and avoid enemies by navigating Charmander with your cursor. You can also pick up powerups along the way!</p>
    <p>Enemies to kill</p>
    <img src="images/grasspoke.png" height="45" width="160">
    <p>Enemies to avoid</p>
    <img src="images/waterpoke.png" height="45" width="160">
    <p>Potion / Attack Speed Boost</p>
    <img src="images/powerups.png" height="45" width="130">
    <p>Finally, there's a secret boss waiting for you at Level 500(if you get there...)</p>
    <img src="images/mewtwowhite.png" height="45" width="45">
    </div>

    <div id="waterwarn">
    <p>In case you weren't paying attention earlier...</p>
    <img src="images/waterpoke.png" height="60" width="220">
    <p>The <span class="blue">water</span> Pokemons are coming out anytime now!</p>
    <p><span class="red">Fire</span> is ineffective against <span class="blue">water</span> so just focus on avoiding them!</p>
    <p>Press 'C' to continue</p>
    </div>

    <div id="psychicwarn">
    <!-- <br> -->
    <img src="images/mewtwo.png" height="80" width="80">
    <p>Feeling invincible?</p>
    <p>Your final test to becoming a pokemon master is to defeat <span class="purple">MEWTWO</span>. Good Luck!</p>
    <p>You will be restored back to full health.</p>
    <p>PROTIP: Do not go too near to <span class="purple">MEWTWO</span></p>
    <p>Press 'C' to continue</p>
    </div>

    <div id="death1">
    <!-- <br> -->
    <img src="images/sad.png" height="80" width="100">
    <p>You died before reaching the Boss level.</p>
    <p>Try harder if you want to be a Pokemon master!</p>
    <p>Press 'R' to restart</p>
    </div>

    <div id="death2">
    <!-- <br> -->
    <img src="images/sad.png" height="80" width="100">
    <p>You died after an intense battle with <span class="purple">MEWTWO</span>.</p>
    <p>You were so close to becoming a Pokemon master!</p>
    <p>Press 'R' to restart</p>
    </div>

    <div id="win">
    <!-- <br> -->
    <img src="images/crown.png" height="100" width="100">
    <p>Congrats on defeating <span class="violet">MEGA MEWTWO</span>!</p>
    <p>You truly are a Pokemon master!</p>
    <p>Press 'R' to challenge yourself again</p>
    </div>

    <div id="evo">
    <!-- <br> -->
    <img src="images/dite.png" height="80" width="80">
    <p>Good job on evolving to <span class="red">Charizard</span>!</p>
    <p>However, leveling up alone won't make you evolve again, you need to collect <span class="red">FIVE</span> Charizardites!</p>
    <p>PROTIP: Charizardites are unlike normal upgrades, they disappear if you don't collect them immediately.</p>
    <p>Press 'C' to continue</p>
    </div>

    <div id="mega">
    <!-- <br> -->
    <img src="images/mega-char.png" height="80" width="80">
    <p>You did it! You evolved to <span class="blue">MEGA </span><span class="red">Charizard</span>!</p>
    <p>Now you can deal with those pesky water Pokemons with your newly acquired <span class="blue"> FLAMES</span>.</p>
    <p>Press 'C' to continue</p>
    </div>

    <div id="mewBox">
    <p>Uh Oh...</p>
    <img src="images/megamew.png" height="100" width="100">
    <p>You've angered <span class="purple">MEWTWO</span>!</p>
    <p><span class="purple">MEWTWO</span> evolves into <span class="violet">MEGA MEWTWO</span> and uses recover!</p>
    <p><span class="violet">MEGA MEWTWO </span>stops all upgrades from spawning and disables all of your movelist!</p>
    <p>Press 'C' to continue</p>
    </div>

    <div id="mew151Box">
    <p>A wild <span class="violet">MEW</span> appears!</p>
    <img src="images/smallmew.png" height="80" width="80">
    <p><span class="violet">MEW</span> restores you back to full health!</p>
    <p><span class="violet">MEW</span> teaches you a new move: <span class="blue">FIREBLAST</span>!</p>
    <p>Press <span class="red">'F'</span> to trigger your new move.</p>
    <p>PROTIP: Approach <span class="violet">MEW</span> whenever you need your health to be restored!</p>
    <p>Press 'C' to continue</p>
    </div>

    <div id="fieldBox">
    <img src="images/fieldmew.png" height="120" width="120">
    <p><span class="violet">MEGA MEWTWO</span> generates a <span class="violet">FORCEFIELD</span> to absorb your attacks!</p>
    <p><span class="violet">MEGA MEWTWO</span> will <span class="red">DRAIN</span> your health if you attack him while the <span class="violet">FORCEFIELD</span> is active.</p>
    <p>However, the <span class="violet">FORCEFIELD</span> won't last forever!</p>
    <p>So time your attacks carefully!</p>
    <p>Press 'C' to continue</p>
    </div>

